Within <https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/cms/hubl/variables|Domain security settings>, can anyone confirm or not if the Content-Security-Policy-Report-Only “nonce” is meant to work on inline-styles?

I see it working on scripts;

```&lt;script nonce="vYfs....."&gt;```
But not on styles;

```&lt;style&gt;```
